Orion Mine Finance Fund I (f.n.a RK Mine Finance (Master) Fund II L.P.) has a gross revenue royalty on the Lithium
Nevada Property in the amount of 8% of gross revenue until aggregate royalty payments equal US$22 million have been paid, at with time the royal will be reduced to 4.0% of the gross revenue on all minerals mined, produced or otherwise
recovered. LNC can at any time elect to reduce the rate of the royalty to 1.75% on notice and payment of US$22 million to Orion;

